{"tid":95862,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【地質公園點火】萬宜東壩生火煮食　遭遊人揭發「聲大夾惡」回敬","createTime":"2017-01-26T10:55:15.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-26T12:12:57.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"28440a41a4a7afbba2dbcb0b01c03575538095ea","tid":95862,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T10:55:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%86%B1%E8%A9%B1/67975/-%E5%9C%B0%E8%B3%AA%E5%85%AC%E5%9C%92%E9%BB%9E%E7%81%AB-%E8%90%AC%E5%AE%9C%E6%9D%B1%E5%A3%A9%E7%94%9F%E7%81%AB%E7%85%AE%E9%A3%9F-%E9%81%AD%E9%81%8A%E4%BA%BA%E6%8F%AD%E7%99%BC-%E8%81%B2%E5%A4%A7%E5%A4%BE%E6%83%A1-%E5%8F%8D%E6%93%8A?utm_content=buffer59aac&amp;utm_medium=Social&amp;utm_source=facebook+hk01&amp;utm_campaign=buffer\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%2586%25B1%25E8%25A9%25B1%2F67975%2F-%25E5%259C%25B0%25E8%25B3%25AA%25E5%2585%25AC%25E5%259C%2592%25E9%25BB%259E%25E7%2581%25AB-%25E8%2590%25AC%25E5%25AE%259C%25E6%259D%25B1%25E5%25A3%25A9%25E7%2594%259F%25E7%2581%25AB%25E7%2585%25AE%25E9%25A3%259F-%25E9%2581%25AD%25E9%2581%258A%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%258F%25AD%25E7%2599%25BC-%25E8%2581%25B2%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%25A4%25BE%25E6%2583%25A1-%25E5%258F%258D%25E6%2593%258A%3Futm_content%3Dbuffer59aac%26utm_medium%3DSocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%2Bhk01%26utm_campaign%3Dbuffer&d=eweu%2BmSeRtL8pKBwkrlkFXvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=df22c601\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%86%B1%E8%A9%B1/67975/-%E5%9C%B0%E8%B3%AA%E5%85%AC%E5%9C%92%E9%BB%9E%E7%81%AB-%E8%90%AC%E5%AE%9C%E6%9D%B1%E5%A3%A9%E7%94%9F%E7%81%AB%E7%85%AE%E9%A3%9F-%E9%81%AD%E9%81%8A%E4%BA%BA%E6%8F%AD%E7%99%BC-%E8%81%B2%E5%A4%A7%E5%A4%BE%E6%83%A1-%E5%8F%8D%E6%93%8A?utm_content=buffer59aac&amp;utm_medium=Social&amp;utm_source=facebook+hk01&amp;utm_campaign=buffer</a><br />\n「每一寸郊野公園土地，我哋都珍而重之」野外動向創辦人陳嘉俊，日前在地質公園萬宜水庫東壩，目擊有遊人生火煮食，當場喝止反遭對方以廣東話「聲大夾惡」回敬，坦言「估唔到香港人都咁不講理」。 <br />\n萬宜水庫一帶是香港地質公園八個景區之一，東壩更加是遊人必到之地。專門籌辦野外活動及訓練的野外動向（HK Discovery）創辦人陳嘉俊，星期一（23日）整天在東壩拍攝地質環境，豈料在黃昏離開時，發現水壩位置冒出白煙，看到有5至6名男女在生火煮食。 <br />\n陳嘉俊第一時間大聲喝止「呢度係非營地唔准生火，請你哋整熄個爐」，對方起初口頭答應，但再之後竟以廣東話「聲大夾惡」地叫一些「還政於民」等口號，令人難以理解，似在純粹宣洩政見的說話。「如果係外地遊客唔識規矩，都情有可原，估唔到香港人都咁不講理」。 <br />\n陳嘉俊於是通報漁護署，獲回覆會派人前來。但職員來之前，該批人士已急忙乘坐的士離開。「我又唔係執法者，阻唔到佢哋，但見佢哋臨走前都有整熄個爐」。他批評「呢個係意識問題，如果個個都咁唔自律，喺郊野公園生火，燒著成個山頭，燒就好快，復原要好長時間」。 <br />\n<br />\n他又提醒，如果見到有人在非營區生火，應即時勸阻，不果的話則需報警及通報漁護署"},{"pid":"8449c60f5cf8b1662e98d8d7c9f3cda062c0939f","tid":95862,"uid":52605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T11:25:32.000Z","msg":"係都粗口屌老母果D啦 無端端叫咩政治口號 都唔啦更<br />\n作故仔咩"},{"pid":"ab179f0a5c998c9704cc78a77efffb98671a4d9e","tid":95862,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T12:03:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c093ebaf78f68eceb6d07247f9a184629f557c5a","tid":95862,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T12:07:53.000Z","msg":"流氓<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e7e31d49cd51639eb4ff7429309d8e9a3f5ea65","tid":95862,"uid":30487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T12:12:57.000Z","msg":"大家都是中國人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}